            "body": "I think unsigned int is much more common so changing this doesn't seem like a good idea. But you can easily do it yourself: Subclass `IntegerConverter` and set `regex = r'-?\\d+'` on the class:\r\n\r\n```python\r\nclass SignedIntConverter(IntegerConverter):\r\n    regex = r'-?\\d+'\r\n\r\napp.url_map.converters['signed_int'] = SignedIntConverter\r\n```\r\n\r\nthen use `<signed_int:user_id>` in your route."
        },
